up|52|pf|y|at|mitche: Play: Well, we have some stuff to discuss
Let's start with asking - "how does declarer plan the play?"
First - count losers in the hand with more trump (the "master hand")
Declarer has 1 sure heart, 1 diamond, and 3 clubs to lose
That is two too many|
