nt||at|mitche: So we need to look for a way to eliminate 2 of those losers.
We see that dummy can't do anything about the @H or @D losers, 
so we need to use dummy's trumps to get rid of 2 of the clubs
We should win the first trick with the @HA - because we have 7 hearts and LHO bid the suit at the 2 level.
West should have at least 5 and possibly 6 hearts. So ducking the first trick means we might see our @HA ruffed out|
